[
    {
        "text": "How Can We End Poverty?",
        "startTime": 795,
        "endTime": 2345,
        "slowStartTime": 1342,
        "slowEndTime": 3742
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever I talk about microcredit,...",
        "startTime": 3967,
        "endTime": 6199,
        "slowStartTime": 6101,
        "slowEndTime": 9524
    },
    {
        "text": "...people say things like, \"I'm sorry, could you repeat that?\"",
        "startTime": 6523,
        "endTime": 9598,
        "slowStartTime": 9935,
        "slowEndTime": 14622
    },
    {
        "text": "...or \"Could you run that by me again?\"",
        "startTime": 9737,
        "endTime": 11939,
        "slowStartTime": 14755,
        "slowEndTime": 18134
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess not many people have heard of it.",
        "startTime": 12992,
        "endTime": 14921,
        "slowStartTime": 19638,
        "slowEndTime": 22606
    },
    {
        "text": "Microcredit is a great way to help poor people lift themselves out of poverty.",
        "startTime": 15488,
        "endTime": 19792,
        "slowStartTime": 23382,
        "slowEndTime": 29913
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a system that offers loans under 200 dollars without collateral...",
        "startTime": 20639,
        "endTime": 25002,
        "slowStartTime": 31109,
        "slowEndTime": 37728
    },
    {
        "text": "...and has changed the lives of millions of people worldwide.",
        "startTime": 25391,
        "endTime": 28615,
        "slowStartTime": 38236,
        "slowEndTime": 43147
    },
    {
        "text": "About 50% of the world population lives under poverty...",
        "startTime": 29770,
        "endTime": 33311,
        "slowStartTime": 44805,
        "slowEndTime": 50191
    },
    {
        "text": "...and struggles to survive on a daily basis.",
        "startTime": 33628,
        "endTime": 36279,
        "slowStartTime": 50592,
        "slowEndTime": 54643
    },
    {
        "text": "But there can be so many creative ways that you can make a difference in the lives of the poor.",
        "startTime": 37085,
        "endTime": 42049,
        "slowStartTime": 55778,
        "slowEndTime": 63298
    },
    {
        "text": "What can you do to help create a poverty - free world?",
        "startTime": 42990,
        "endTime": 45707,
        "slowStartTime": 64635,
        "slowEndTime": 68786
    },
    {
        "text": "Any ideas?",
        "startTime": 46207,
        "endTime": 47105,
        "slowStartTime": 69461,
        "slowEndTime": 70882
    },
    {
        "text": "I think many of the problems of the developing nations have to do with infrastructure.",
        "startTime": 47623,
        "endTime": 52145,
        "slowStartTime": 71584,
        "slowEndTime": 78442
    },
    {
        "text": "If there are no roads, food, medicine and other needed goods and services cannot reach the people.",
        "startTime": 52422,
        "endTime": 57765,
        "slowStartTime": 78783,
        "slowEndTime": 86872
    },
    {
        "text": "At some point, it is the responsibility of a good government...",
        "startTime": 58577,
        "endTime": 61933,
        "slowStartTime": 88015,
        "slowEndTime": 93124
    },
    {
        "text": "...to employ people to build roads and water purification systems and other necessary facilities.",
        "startTime": 62000,
        "endTime": 67601,
        "slowStartTime": 93150,
        "slowEndTime": 101627
    }
]